it was gonna

15:07.267 --> 15:10.133
be all right,
with what I went through,
and you know that, right?

15:10.167 --> 15:11.633
-Stay right here.
Stay right here.
-Remember?

15:11.667 --> 15:13.167
-What do you mean,
he held you tight?

15:13.200 --> 15:15.800
-He laid with me
every night and told me
that I was gonna be okay,

15:15.833 --> 15:18.067
'cause of what happened
with me and what's-his-nuts,
you remember.

15:18.067 --> 15:20.700
When you were out
over there, and I was
over there, with dinner,

15:20.733 --> 15:21.933
whoa, whoa, whoa?

15:21.967 --> 15:23.533
-(radio chatter)
-When was the last time
you used?

15:23.567 --> 15:25.333
-I have got a lot goin' on,
so leave me alone,

15:25.367 --> 15:27.767
and don't ask me questions
like that, 'cause this has
nothin' to do with that.

15:27.800 --> 15:30.067
-Oh.
-What happened was
I called 9-1-1.

15:30.067 --> 15:31.967
Look at my windshield
of my car.

15:32.067 --> 15:33.767
-I know.
I will when my partner
gets here.

15:33.800 --> 15:35.533
-Look at my car.
And why aren't they
gettin' talked to

15:35.567 --> 15:37.533
about meth
and whoa, whoa, whoa.
-I'm going to in a minute.

15:37.567 --> 15:40.067
-(bleep) Hamburger Helper
with a burn barrel,

15:40.067 --> 15:41.133
