so I can talk to them?

15:48.833 --> 15:50.433
-Sure.
-Can I get
my cigarettes back, sir?

15:50.467 --> 15:52.767
-No, you're gonna stay
right there.
-I know.

15:52.800 --> 15:53.967
-What's goin' on, guys?

15:54.067 --> 15:55.833
Is she usually like this?
