-No.

16:12.967 --> 16:16.533
I mean...
what would you say?

16:16.567 --> 16:19.433
-Were you guys intimate?
-I guess you could say that.

16:19.467 --> 16:22.933
-Okay.
-But, I mean, she's been--
she's been stayin' here

16:22.967 --> 16:25.533
'cause, uh, I guess
she got kicked out
of her dad's...

16:25.567 --> 16:26.867
-Okay.
-...a couple times.

16:26.900 --> 16:29.500
-Was there any hands
put on each other?
Did she hit you?

16:29.533 --> 16:31.867
-Man: No, she didn't hit me.
