16:31.900 --> 16:33.500
She pushed me once.
-Anderson: She did push you?

16:33.533 --> 16:37.067
How'd she get soaked?
-Woman: She was talkin'
her smack, and we just--

16:37.100 --> 16:39.733
-She kept running her mouth
and calling us all kinds of--
