16:56.067 --> 16:58.367
-Do me a favor
and have a seat for me.

16:58.400 --> 16:59.467
Erin?
-Yes?

16:59.500 --> 17:00.867
-He sprayed you
with the hose, correct?

17:00.900 --> 17:02.667
-Yeah, he said,
