They all sit

17:22.600 --> 17:24.767
and watch the show,
and I take care of it.

17:24.800 --> 17:26.267
-Okay.
-I have their backs.

17:26.300 --> 17:29.067
-Pops, come over here.
How'd you get a cut
on your eye?

17:29.067 --> 17:32.233
-My son's girlfriend
hit me right in the face
a little while ago.

17:32.267 --> 17:35.500
-She did?
-Yeah, she's been drunk here
the last couple hours,

17:35.533 --> 17:37.967
just causin' trouble,
screamin' and fightin'.
-Okay.

17:38.067 --> 17:39.867
-Insultin' us, and, uh, so on
and so forth.
-Okay.

17:39.900 --> 17:41.900
Well, there we go.
-She ran over and hit me
right in the face.

17:41.933 --> 17:44.133
She even attacked my wife,
she tried to come up
in the trailer here.

17:44.167 --> 17:45.967
-Okay.
Y-- You guys
all live together, right?

17:46.067 --> 17:48.133
-Uh, no, sir.
Just my wife, my son,
and myself.

17:48.167 --> 17:50.167
And she's not my son,
and she just has a lab.

17:50.200 --> 17:52.133
You know, I mean,
I'm sure anybody
that acts like that,

17:52.167 --> 17:54.700
they gotta be,
you know, on something.

17:54.733 --> 17:56.133
-I got a question for you.
-Yes, sir.

17:56.167 --> 17:58.200
-Do you use any type
of illegal narcotics?

17:58.233 --> 17:59.700
-No, sir, I don't.

17:59.733 --> 18:01.667
-Not methamphetamine,
nothin' like that?
-No, sir, not at all.

18:01.700 --> 18:04.467
-Okay.
-No, I got a pulled shoulder,
and I am takin' some, uh,

18:04.500 --> 18:06.600
ibuprofen and they gave me
some other kind of pills...

18:06.633 --> 18:08.700
-Okay.
-...that I'm takin'
for my shoulder, but that's it.

18:08.733 --> 18:11.367
-Okay.
All right, do you mind
steppin' over here for me

18:11.400 --> 18:14.833
